== Aho biherereye ==
urugomero rw’amashanyarazi ruherereye ku mugezi wa Ruzizi, unyura ku mupaka uhuriweho n’u [[Rwanda]] na [[Repubulika Iharanira Demokarasi ya Kongo]] (RDC). Aho iherereye ni 5 kilometres (3 mi) mu burengerazuba bw'umujyi wa Bugarama, mu [[Akarere ka Rusizi|Karere ka Rusizi]], mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|Ntara y'Uburengerazuba bw'u Rwanda]], hafi 267 kilometres (166 mi), mu majyepfo y'uburengerazuba bwa [[Kigali]], umurwa mukuru w'u Rwanda. <ref>http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Rwanda_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Kigali&toplace=Bugarama%2C%20Western%20Province%2C%20Rwanda%2C&dt1=ChIJl-fYjiWk3BkRyAsdQaU2K_M&dt2=ChIJF2WipJCKwhkRNvQV4NPpALs</ref> Imirongo igereranya ya Ruzizi ya III Yamashanyarazi ni:  <ref>https://www.google.com/maps/place/2%C2%B042'05.0%22S+28%C2%B057'56.0%22E/@-2.7102568,28.9783899,12.83z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x0!8m2!3d-2.7013889!4d28.9655556</ref>

== Incamake ==
urugomero rw’amashanyarazii ni urwa gatatu muri casade y'amashanyarazi ku ruzi rwa Ruzizi, igirira akamaro ibihugu [[Uburundi|by'Uburundi]], DRC n'u Rwanda. Amashanyarazi arimo Ruzizi I (megawatt 29.8) na Ruzizi II (megawatt 43.8), byombi biherereye mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bwa Ruzizi ya III kandi byombi bikora guhera muri Kamena 2017.  Imbaraga zitangwa zizagabanywa mubihugu bitatu binyuze mumiyoboro isanzwe yo gukwirakwiza, ihujwe na Ruzizi I na Ruzizi II. Amashanyarazi yombi hamwe numuyoboro wohereza bizasubirwamo. Biteganijwe ko u Rwanda rwakira megawatt 50 na megawatt 147 zavuye kuri Ruzizi III. <ref name="Grey">https://www.esi-africa.com/news/rwanda-secures-grant-increase-share-ruzizi-iii-project/</ref>

== Inkunga ==
Kugeza mu Kuboza 2015, amafaranga yo kubaka yabazwe ni miliyoni 625.19 US $.  Muri ibyo, "miliyoni 138.88 z'amadolari y'Amerika zizatangwa na Leta aturutse muri AfDB na miliyoni 50.22 z'amadorali yavuye mubikorera". <ref name="Bud" /> Abandi baterankunga barimo Banki y’ishoramari y’i Burayi, <ref>https://ec.europa.eu/europeaid/ruzizi-hydropower-plant_en</ref> KfW <ref name="Bud" /> na Banki y'Isi .  Raporo iheruka gushyira igiciro cya miliyoni 450 $.  Gufunga gutanga amafaranga biteganijwe ko bizagerwaho hagati ya 2021. <ref>https://www.vivafrik.com/2020/03/02/energie-propre-10-millions-de-congolais-beneficieront-du-projet-ruzizi-iii-a35015.html</ref>

== Abashinzwe iterambere ==
Muri Kanama 2019, byavuzwe ko guverinoma eshatu z’Afurika bireba zahisemo Scatec (yahoze yitwa SN Power ) na Serivisi ishinzwe guteza imbere inganda (IPS) kugira ngo ikore uyu mushinga w’ibikorwa remezo by’ingufu zishobora kuvugururwa. , ingufu zitangwa hano biteganijwe ko zizatwara amadolari ya Amerika 0.11 na US $ 0.13 kuri kilo Watthour yingufu. Abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 30 bazabyungukiramo. <ref name="9R">https://www.afrik21.africa/en/east-africa-sn-power-and-ips-will-develop-ruzizi-iii-dam-project/</ref>

